</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="5.[151,1437,152,924]" pageId="5" pageNumber="31">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[196,299,823,849]" pageId="5" pageNumber="31">Habitat.</emphasis>
This species was collected in very small and very shallow streams with silt bottomed pools with rich leaf deposits, rather shaded.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
